      <h1>Chapter 1: Children of Solace</h1>
      
      <div class="text">
        <p>
       
The span of evil begun at dawn,<br>
From the edge of the gate came the guardian in waiting.<br>
With the blood to bind our eyes beyond the boundary.


        </p>
        <p>
      The watcher as a crow came to draw the moss ridden tower.<br>
Ruler of winter, thy veiled one is weary and wise.<br>
She who shines the storms of end year and holds the whole heart of stones in the cold.
        </p>
        <p>
      The water flows beyond the edge, pouring into the crystal sphere of the night.<br>
War weighs on her shoulder,<br>
Circling the center-<br>
Of the kings brigade.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      
      
